# THOR — AI Landing Page Generator
# Cursor Rules — Captain's Standing Orders

## IDENTITY
- **Product**: Thor — AI-powered landing page generator
- **Audience**: Business professionals and owners across fitness, legal, medical, finance, SaaS, hospitality, beauty, language schools, and community sectors.

## RULES — ALWAYS APPLY WITHOUT BEING TOLD
1. **RESPONSIVE FIRST**: every component mobile-first.
   - Mobile < 640px, Tablet 640-1024px, Desktop > 1024px
   - Use Tailwind `sm:` `md:` `lg:` prefixes on everything.

2. **NO DROPDOWNS**: ever. Use card selectors or pills.

3. **NO EMOJIS**: use icons only (Lucide React or inline SVG when Lucide lacks a required brand mark).

4. **NO DUPLICATE CTAs**: one call to action per screen.

5. **NO FOCUS RINGS**: `outline-none focus:outline-none focus:ring-0` on all interactive elements.

6. **NO BROWSER DEFAULTS** bleeding through on any element.

7. **DARK + LIGHT MODE**: every component must support both.
   - Use theme-aware Tailwind classes (and/or CSS variables where appropriate).

8. **PREMIUM QUALITY CHECK**: before finishing any component ask:
   - “Would Apple’s California design team ship this?”
   - If no, improve it.

9. **ANIMATIONS**: subtle only.
   - Never animate layout properties.
   - Use `transform` and `opacity` only.
   - Duration 150–300ms for interactions.
   - Duration 2–4s for ambient animations.

10. **MODALS** always:
   - `max-w-xl`, `rounded-2xl`, backdrop-blur overlay
   - `bg-black/60` backdrop, overflow-y-auto, `max-h-[90vh]`
   - `p-8`, `gap-4` between elements
   - Never clip card borders. Keep padding around selector grids.

11. **PERFORMANCE**:
   - `will-change: transform` on animated elements.
   - CSS transforms only, never animate layout properties.

12. **ONE DIRECTION**:
   - Don’t suggest alternatives unless asked.
   - Execute the brief precisely.

13. **SCREENSHOT-AS-SPEC**:
   - When the user provides a reference screenshot, treat it as a binding UI spec for hierarchy, spacing, and interaction.
   - Do not add extra UI (badges, promos, featured rings) unless explicitly requested.

---

# Thor — Design System (2026 Premium)

Apple precision, Norse power. Every new component MUST follow this system.

## Typography

Load via `next/font/google` in `app/layout.tsx`:

| Role | Font | Weights | CSS variable |
|------|------|---------|--------------|
| Headlines / wordmark | Fraunces | 300, 400, 700, 900 | `--font-fraunces` |
| UI, body, buttons | Inter | 400, 500, 600 | `--font-inter` |

- Body default: `font-sans` → Inter
- Display / headlines: `font-display` → Fraunces
- Never use Geist or system serif for marketing headlines

## Color tokens

| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|--------|
| Lightning Blue (primary) | `#0EA5E9` | Icons, accents, Mjolnir line |
| Storm Gold (accent) | `#EAB308` | Selected cards/pills, active step dots |
| Storm Sky (dark bg) | `#0A0F1E` | Dark page background, dark navbar scroll |
| Card/modal dark | `#111827` | Dark modals, cards, selector tiles |
| Border dark | `#1E293B` | Dark borders, inactive dots |
| Text primary dark | `#F8FAFC` | Headlines & primary text on dark |
| Text secondary dark | `#64748B` | Muted copy, placeholders on dark |
| Light background | `#FFFFFF` | Light page |
| Light card/modal | `#F8FAFC` | Light modals, cards |
| Light border | `#E2E8F0` | Light borders |
| Light navbar border | `#F1F5F9` | Light navbar bottom border |
| Text primary light | `#0A0F1E` | Body/UI on light |
| Hero headline light | `#0F172A` | Hero headline only (light mode) |
| Hero subheadline light | `#94A3B8` | Hero subheadline (light mode) |
| Hero subheadline dark | `#64748B` | Hero subheadline (dark mode) |
| Selected tint | `rgba(234, 179, 8, 0.08)` | Selected card/pill background |
| Hover tint | `rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.05)` | Card/pill hover background |

## Dark mode

- Page background: `#0A0F1E`
- Navbar: transparent at top → `#0A0F1E/90` + `backdrop-blur-md` on scroll
- Modal/card: `#111827`, border `#1E293B`
- Text primary: `#F8FAFC`, secondary: `#64748B`

## Light mode

- Page background: `#FFFFFF`
- Navbar: white + `border-bottom 1px #F1F5F9` (always or on scroll per implementation)
- Modal/card: `#F8FAFC`, border `#E2E8F0`
- Text primary: `#0A0F1E`, secondary: `#64748B`

## Theme

- Toggle: Sun (dark mode) / Moon (light mode), Lucide, 20px (`h-5 w-5`)
- Persist: `localStorage` key `thor-theme` (`dark` | `light`)
- Transitions: `300ms ease-in-out` on color/background changes

## Navbar

- Font: Inter throughout
- Wordmark “Thor”: Fraunces 700, 22px (`font-display text-[22px] font-bold`)
- Lightning bolt: Lucide `Zap`, `#0EA5E9`, 20px, before wordmark
- Sign in: Inter 500, 15px
- **No** Get Started in navbar — hero CTA only
- Right: Sign in + theme toggle

## Hero

- Layout: centered, `max-w-4xl`, `min-h-[100dvh]`, vertical center
- **No** aurora, gradients, or mouse-follow effects on hero
- Headline (Fraunces 900):
  - Line 1: “For the ones who”
  - Line 2: “mean ” + accent “business.” in `#0EA5E9`
  - Sizes: 88px desktop (`lg:`), 56px tablet (`sm:`), 40px mobile
  - `tracking-[-0.02em]`, `leading-none`, `max-w-[720px]` centered
  - Dark: `#F8FAFC`, Light: `#0F172A`
- Subheadline (Inter 400): 18px desktop (`lg:text-lg`), 16px mobile (`text-base`), `max-w-[440px]`, `mt-6` (24px)
- **Mjolnir edge**: 1px × 120px horizontal line, `#0EA5E9`, `opacity-40`, centered between subheadline and CTA (`mt-6` after subheadline)
- Get Started button:
  - Inter 600, `h-[52px]`, `px-10`, `rounded-full`, bg `#0EA5E9`, white text
  - Hover: `#0284C7`, `scale-[1.02]`, `transition-all duration-200 ease-out`
  - `mt-11` (44px) below Mjolnir line
  - No border

## Modals

- Backdrop: `bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-sm`
- Theme-aware shell (see dark/light tokens above)
- 6 steps; carousel `w-[600%]`; gold active step dot
- Card selectors: 2 col mobile, 3 col `sm+`, heights 80/90/100px
- Default card border `#334155` (dark) / `#E2E8F0` (light)
- Hover: 1.5px `#0EA5E9` border + blue tint + scale 1.02
- Selected: 1.5px `#EAB308` border + gold tint
- Icons on cards: 20px `#0EA5E9`
- No focus rings on cards: `outline-none focus:ring-0`

## Buttons

- Primary (Claude-style): bg `#0A0F1E`, white text, hover `#111827`
- Thor blue `#0EA5E9` is an accent color, not the default button fill
- Storm Gold `#EAB308` reserved for selection states, not primary button hover
- Min tap target: 44px (`min-h-11`)
- No focus rings (see standing orders above)

## Implementation rules

- Copy lives in structured `copy` objects — no hardcoded visible strings in JSX
- Tailwind arbitrary values: `bg-[#0EA5E9]`, etc.
- Mobile-first (`sm:`, `lg:`)
- No dropdowns — cards or pills only
- Do NOT use green/emerald palette
- Do NOT reintroduce aurora or animated hero backgrounds

## TECH STACK
- Next.js App Router
- Tailwind CSS
- Lucide React icons
- Fraunces + Inter from Google Fonts
- Supabase (Week 2)
- Claude API via `/api/generate` route

